{"tid":1621244,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"安已不 54歲婦疑染伊波拉病毒 唔通真係講中咗？","createTime":"2019-10-04T12:55:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T14:45:41.000Z","uid":183147,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"dc6a132af1e5fe255e961748c9c77a9834a85c0b","tid":1621244,"uid":183147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T12:55:51.000Z","msg":"衞生防護中心公布，今日(4日)接獲一宗伊波拉病毒病懷疑個案的呈報，涉事54歲女病人自昨(3日)起出現頭痛、暈眩、發燒、嘔吐和腹瀉，同日到瑪嘉烈醫院急症室求醫，隨即入院接受隔離治療，現時情況穩定。<br />\n<br />\n防護中心表示，在接獲個案呈報後，中心立即展開流行病學調查，並安排採集病人的血液樣本進行檢測。病人的血液樣本經檢驗後，證實對伊波拉病毒呈陰性反應。中心會根據世界衞生組織指引安排病人於兩天後接受血液覆檢，以排除病人感染伊波拉病毒。<br />\n<br />\n初步調查顯示，病人曾於5月27日至9月14日到訪剛果民主共和國金沙薩，期間沒有接觸不適人士，亦沒有到訪醫療設施或受影響省份，其同行人士和家居接觸者至今沒有出現病徵。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/04/205304_cbe169598ed688b2f74f96516a095000.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F04%2F205304_cbe169598ed688b2f74f96516a095000.png&h=e0084f6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一時間諗到呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知咩嘅去睇睇！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1615112/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1615112/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"6edd0bb0c3c167a5443c072a6c55df233c30d6cf","tid":1621244,"uid":96648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T12:57:12.000Z","msg":"細菌戰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1619230\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1619230</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"37670477e67347c0efe428aed7ff788252164c24","tid":1621244,"uid":183147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T13:02:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191004/mobile/bkn-20191004172943254-1004_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2